### Variables
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/books
@bookId = 9
@bookSlug = 9_book
@year = 2026
@start = 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z
@end = 2026-12-31T23:59:59Z

### Leituras do ano (UTC)
GET {{baseUrl}}/year/{{year}}
Accept: application/json

### Detalhes do livro
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{bookId}}
Accept: application/json

### Detalhes do livro por slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/slug/{{bookSlug}}
Accept: application/json

### Lista de leituras (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/list?status=read&limit=20
Accept: application/json

### Próxima página de leituras
GET {{baseUrl}}/list?status=read&limit=20&cursor=id:123
Accept: application/json

### Busca (livros + autores)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=ursula&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Resumo mensal
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?range=month
Accept: application/json

### Resumo anual
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?range=year
Accept: application/json

### Resumo personalizado
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?range=custom&start={{start}}&end={{end}}
Accept: application/json
